settings.text:
What happens when two farms, deeply passionate about their craft, join forces? You get a natural, delicious product crafted with care, and that's something we take pride in.

That's why the delectable milk for our treats comes from our friends at Sutton Milk in South Florida — a true haven for cows. You can even visit them and see for yourself.

Hence, our milk is made up of 50% love.

The most delicious yogurt is the one that's freshly made. That's why this unique dessert is prepared on-site for you with milk from happy cows.

Want to add fruits? No problem. Don't consume sugar? We'll find an alternative option for you.

The foundation for our casseroles is Ukrainian raw-stuff combined with products from Sutton Milk.

Each piece of this casserole is rich in natural protein and has a low calorie concentration.

And to make it even more delicious, try a piece of casseroles with hot coffee.
Soft and delicate layers, fluffy frosting, natural fillings without flavor enhancers — cakes made from the farmers milk taste just like home.

This flavor is undoubtedly familiar to you from childhood. That's because we create the most delicious ice cream from natural dairy products of our own production, berries, and fruits.

A tender, creamy texture with homely tastes in a modern rendition without added sugar. You'll want to come back for more of this ice cream.

Start your day properly with nutritious breakfasts.

Maybe a crispy croissant with natural jam? Or perhaps a hearty sandwich or a fresh salad?

Choose what suits your taste the most. Because the main ingredient everywhere is care from the farmer.

How about a cup of fragrant coffee?

Freshly ground with the addition of natural farmer's milk. You won't find any equivalents to this coffee anywhere on the entire southern coast.
